    description:"Implement Merge Sort — a stable, divide-and-conquer sorting algorithm.\n\nAlgorithm:\n1. Divide the array into two halves\n2. Recursively sort each half\n3. Merge the two sorted halves using a two-pointer technique\n\nTime: O(n log n) in all cases. Space: O(n) for the merge buffer. Merge sort is the preferred choice when stability is required.",
